              <h4>FeelGreateFoodie February 1st 2018: </h4>
              <p>This place feels like Boulder. It's got a small town restaurant feel but the menu is local, fresh, and awesome. Lots of specials, good beers on tap, and the service is 10/10. Swing by and grab everything.</p>
